# Self-learning data directory.
#
# The WAF's learning pipeline stores collected samples here:
#   - collected_attacks.csv  — requests blocked by rules/AI (confirmed attacks)
#   - collected_benign.csv   — sampled allowed requests (baseline normal traffic)
#   - merged_training_data.csv — combined dataset used for retraining
#
# Archived files (after retraining) are preserved with timestamp suffixes
# for forensic analysis.
#
# This data is auto-generated at runtime. Do not commit data files to git.
